The file COPYING-GPLv3 contains a copy of the License.

[Libraries with licensing information]
chatnut uses GTK+ which is licensed under version 2.1 of the GNU
Lesser General Public License. The file COPYING-LGPLv2.1 contains
a copy of the License.

